Class LMSObtainQueryWithFormMethod

java.lang.Object
  jcolibri.method.gui.formFilling.ObtainQueryWithFormMethod
      main.userinterface.LMSObtainQueryWithFormMethod

public class LMSObtainQueryWithFormMethod
extends jcolibri.method.gui.formFilling.ObtainQueryWithFormMethod

Shows a from to obtain the query.
The methods of this class allow to use default values (read from the query), hide some attributes and specify the label shown with each attribute.

Version:
1.1
Author:
